   <concept id="FAR_22_202" class="- topic/topic concept/concept " xtrc="">
      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">22.202</ph> Contract clause.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p id="d1308e8" class="- topic/p ">Insert the clause at <xref href="52.222-3.dita#FAR_52_222_3"
                  base="i1055332"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref ">52.222-3</xref>, Convict Labor,	in solicitations and contracts above the micro-purchase threshold,	when the contract will be performed in the United States, Puerto	Rico, the Northern Mariana Islands, American Samoa, Guam, or the	U.S. Virgin Islands; unless-</p>
         <ol id="d1278e22" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1314e15">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
						            The	contract will be subject to <xref href="http://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=granuleid%3AUSC-prelim-title41-chapter65&amp;saved=%7CZ3JhbnVsZWlkOlVTQy1wcmVsaW0tdGl0bGU0MC1jaGFwdGVyMzctZnJvbnQ%3D%7C%7C%7C0%7Cfalse%7Cprelim&amp;edition=prelim"
                        scope="external"
                        format="html">41 U.S.C. chapter 65</xref>, (see <xref href="Subpart_22.6.dita#FAR_Subpart_22_6"
                        base="i1097464"
                        outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                        class="- topic/xref ">subpart  22.6</xref>), which	contains a separate prohibition against the employment of convict	labor;</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1314e26">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
						            The supplies	or services are to be purchased from Federal Prison Industries,	Inc. (see <xref href="Subpart_8.6.dita#FAR_Subpart_8_6"
                        base="i1117091"
                        outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                        class="- topic/xref ">subpart  8.6</xref>); or</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1314e34">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
						            The acquisition	involves the purchase, from any State prison, of finished supplies	that may be secured in the open market or from existing stocks,	as distinguished from supplies requiring special fabrication.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
